        correct: 1,
        rationale: "SSRIs require 4-6 weeks at adequate dose for full therapeutic effect due to 5-HT1A autoreceptor desensitization. At 3 weeks, the medication has not had sufficient time for efficacy assessment. The NP should continue the current dose and reassess at 6 weeks before concluding treatment failure."
